source.name: ED Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) Annual Report - FY2009
source.description: This file contains the FY 2009 FOIA annual report of the U.S. Department of Education (ED). The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2009. It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
